data.description: Enjoy the Central Florida lifestyle in this beautiful home located in the desirable community of Hammock Pointe. Highlighted by excellent curb appeal, mature landscaping and situated on an elevated lot. Featuring an open floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, guest bath, office/den, living room, dining room, fireplace, loft, laundry room with utility sink and plenty of storage. A stunning entrance will welcome you with ceramic tile floors throughout the first level, volume ceilings, surround sound and plenty of natural light. The gourmet kitchen is ideal for the aspiring chef in your family - featuring 42" light cabinets with quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, flat cooktop, built-in double ovens and breakfast nook. The living room is the focal point of this home - ideal for entertaining family and friends! The master retreat is on the main floor, featuring a spa-like master bath, dual sinks, walk-in shower and jetted tub. Secondary bedrooms are situated on the second level along with a spacious loft and wet bar.  Extend your living area outdoors with an expansive covered and screened lanai, overlooking a large, fenced yard – very private!  Upgrades include: new roof (Jan 2023), new dishwasher, new A/C system first floor (Oct 2022), new ceramic tile floors in upstairs ensuite bedroom. Minutes from Lake Nona, Medical City, shopping, restaurants, medical and major roads.
